{
  "stem": "18770.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This case, I think the guy was Jewish who was taking us out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother has the good sense, when the guards come over-- the German guards-- to talk to her and my aunt, to instruct my aunt to act like she doesn't understand a word they are saying.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because both my aunt and my mother speak a perfect German and there is the realization on her part-- which was rather shrewd-- that if they act like they speak or understand German, the German guards might then say, well, God, they understand German because they're Jewish and they speak Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Since Yiddish and German are connected languages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they act like they don't understand them at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My mother actually has refused to part with and has with her a little prayer book which she has hidden back there in that hay wagon.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So which, if that was found, of course the jig would be up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whatever we were taking was, was very little.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of it probably had gone ahead of us because we were, you know, like I said, we didn't all travel together carrying the same things.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have some chocolate bars that are still left from Suchard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I remember that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I'm trying to think if there was anything else specifically.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, but I do remember that on that journey out of Chelm, somebody comes riding up to our wagon-- coming from Chelm up to where we are-- to tell the guy who is, who-- who's Jewish, who was taking us out of there, that the Germans are beginning to round up the Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 54
    }
  ],
